OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'loving, funny'
OL,4,Cteen who died after being struck by car
OL,6,FThe family of an "energetic, funny,
OL,7,Floving" teenager who died after being
OL,8,Fhit by a car have paid tribute.
OL,10,FEthan Allen, 15, was hit by a black
OL,11,FSeat Ibiza on Rochdale Road on at
OL,12,Faround 8:10pm on Tuesday 21 May.
OL,14,FEthan was taken to hospital where he
OL,15,Fremained in critical condition before
OL,16,Fpassing away two days later on 23 May
OL,17,F2024.
