OL,6,FThe driver of the vehicle, a 38-year-
OL,7,Fold man, was arrested at the scene on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of causing serious injury by
OL,9,Fcareless driving and driving under the
OL,10,Finfluence of drugs.
OL,12,FHe has since been released on bail.
OL,14,FPaying tribute to Ethan, his family
OL,15,Fsaid: "Ethan was a very energetic
OL,16,Ffunny loving young boy who always made
OL,17,Ftime for others. He was always
OL,18,Fsmiling. He had a great love of the
OL,19,Fsport basketball and played for Oldham
OL,20,FState Warriors and more recently
OL,21,FRoyton Mavericks.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
