OL,4,Cteen who died after being struck by car
OL,6,F"Ethan also recently became a
OL,7,Fbasketball referee which he was proud
OL,8,Fto do. He attended as a pupil at the
OL,9,FOasis Academy Oldham where he was
OL,10,Fpopular with friends and peers.
OL,12,F"He is truly missed by his parents,
OL,13,FGillian and Gordon, sister Abbie,
OL,14,FGrandmother Eunice, his stepfather,
OL,15,Fand stepbrothers. We thank people for
OL,16,Ftheir continued support and
OL,17,Fcondolences.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
