OL,6,F"Our deepest thoughts and prayers are
OL,7,Fwith the family and friends of our
OL,8,Fdeparted comrade during this
OL,9,Fchallenging time. Your pain is shared,
OL,10,Fand our collective support is
OL,11,Funwavering. Let us come together in
OL,12,Funity and compassion to honor the
OL,13,Flegacy of Ethan."
OL,15,F's serious collision investigators are
OL,16,Fappealing for anyone who may have
OL,17,Fwitnessed the incident to come forward.
